<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"מיהו יהודי" redirects here. For the 1930s catchphrase, see <a href="/wiki/Who%27s_Yehoodi%3F" title="Who&#39;s Yehoodi?">Who's Yehoodi?</a></div>
