<li><a href="/wiki/Israeli_Sign_Language" title="Israeli Sign Language">Shassi</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Judeo-Iranian_languages" title="Judeo-Iranian languages">Judaeo-Iranian</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Judaeo-Spanish" title="Judaeo-Spanish">Ladino</a></li>
